Definition: mercilessness characterized by an unwillingness to relent or let up
Example: the relentlessness or their pursuit
Synonyms: adj, all, implacable, relentless, continual, inexorability, inexorable, inexorableness, inflexible, mercilessness, characterized, by, an, unwillingness, to, relent, or, let, up, the, their, pursuit
Category: noun.attribute
